            "answer_text": "METHOD 1 : Let SP of one chair = \u20b91SP of 27 chairs = \u20b927 Gain on 27 chairs = SP of 27 chairs - CP of 27 chairs SP of 5 chairs = SP of 27 chairs - CP of 27 chairs\u20b95 = \u20b927 - CP of 27 chairs  CP of 27 chairs = \u20b9(27-55) = \u20b922   METHOD 2 : Gain = SP - CP5SP = 27SP - 27CP27CP = 22SP  CP = 22k and SP = 27k, where k is any postive integer.   ",
